      "rationale": "Richardson extrapolation applied to three mesh levels. GCI_fine = 1.8% for NIH at worst-case operating point (3000 RPM, 5 L/min). Asymptotic range ratio 0.98 confirms convergence in the asymptotic regime. Achieved level exceeds requirement."
    },
