      "rationale": "Validation tests performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry at 5 operating points bracketing the clinical CPB range (2.5–6.5 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM). Porcine blood analog properties within 8% of human blood rheology. Geometric fidelity confirmed by CMM inspection (maximum deviation 0.03 mm from nominal CAD)."
