      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; model form selection justified by literature precedent.",
      "rationale": "Reynolds-averaged Navier-Stokes with k-omega SST turbulence closure is the accepted model form for centrifugal blood pump CFD per FDA benchmark study (Hariharan et al. 2011). Non-Newtonian blood rheology modeled via Carreau-Yasuda model with parameters from Cho and Kensey (1991). Model form selection consistent with published best practices."
    },
