      "rationale": "Geometric inputs from manufacturer CAD files (revision D, verified by CMM). Fluid properties from published human blood rheology data (Merrill 1969, Chien 1970). Boundary conditions (flow rates, rotational speeds) from clinical CPB protocols. All inputs documented in simulation data package SDP-2024-003."
    },
